criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-40 years;

          -  Gestational age: ≤ 14 weeks (as judged by the date of the last menstrual period);

          -  Single pregnancy;

          -  Non-lactating;

          -  Planned residence in the area for the duration of the study (3 years).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  TSH levels outside the normal range

          -  History of serious medical conditions such as HIV, hypertension, diabetes, renal,
             hepatic or cardiovascular disease, thyroid disorders, mental disorders;

          -  Use of iodine supplement.
